data.description: One of the best priced home in Plainfield.  Oversized lot on cul de sac. Home built in 1999 and has been well cared for. Large brick patio. Great kitchen area. Family room and kitchen face east for great sunrises. The opportunities are endless with this home!  The kitchen features an abundance of oak cabinets, stainless steel appliances and an eating area - with sliding glass doors to your brick patio and yard. Plenty of windows to bring in the natural light. The living room and dining room add additional entertainment space.  Upstairs you'll find 4 generously sized bedrooms. Owner's suite is complete with a private bathroom with a stand alone shower, and double sinks. The hall bathroom includes a tub/shower combo.  The unfinished (DRY) basement is begging to be revamped and turned into the perfect addition to your living space. Spectacular location - desirable Heritage Meadows Subdivision.
